#31200
the Beginning of the North Star Artery~
   For as far as the naked eye can see the cobblestone path that leads dead
north.  To your south is back to the Kir Drax'in's armored front gates.  The
forest to the west and east is mostly cleared around the tall wall of the
magnificent city.  The road has a wide shoulder covered in pinestraw on either
side.  
~
