#31201
the North Star Artery~
   This is a wide, cobblestone path that continues north as far as you can
see.  To the south, you see the Kir Drax'in City Gates, which are armed to the
teeth.  To the west, and east you find that the forest is more dense than it
is closer to the wall.  
