#31203
the North Star Artery~
   This is a wide, cobblestone path that continues north as far as you can
see.  Looking south you will find that the road continues to the city of Kir
Drax'in.  To the west, and east the forest is very thick and high.  There are
very large firs and pine trees towering over the road.  The trees are trimmed
often to keep the road clear and a good view of the sky.  
