#31212
the North Star Artery~
   This is a wide, cobblestone path that continues north as far as you can
see.  Looking south you will find that the road continues to the city of Kir
Drax'in.  The landscape is beginning to change as the climate starts to become
much colder and less stable.  The trees are becoming more sparse surrounding
the road north.  Plant and animal life seem to be thinning out as well.  
~
