0 0 31799
S
#31226
The Bridge of Frjosa Hel-vgr River~
   You are on the bridge that spans over the Frjosa Hel-vgr River.  There are
only two exits, you may push forward north across the bridge and south to
leave the bridge and back to the road.  To the east and the west, you will
find a frozen torrent of slush, ice and freezing waters.  The water is very
loud, and violent, water is constantly being turned to ice on this bridge.  
It must take a great effort to keep it clear.  
~
