#31230
Approaching the Frjosa Bridge~
   The dull black stone is fading to the remnants of what used to be the North
Star Artery.  You may go east, or west into the fray.  North will bring you to
a barely recognizable pathway and south back to the bridge.  The sound of the
wind and the river is almost deafening.  
~
