#31231
the Remnants of the North Star Artery~
   The cobblestone pathway is all but gone.  There is only a small strip of
the road visible down the center.  This is where the few travellers who are
brave enough to be here have trampled the ice and snow into a sludgy mess of
horse shit, mud and ice.  To the east and west you can not see much except a
barren icy wasteland.  Its colder than a demons ass out here.  The road south
seems the way to go, much safer..  
~
